      "content": "it's just such a constant, heavy ache. i feel like i'm just dragging this weight around every single day for no reason at all. it feels like i'm just waiting for an end that never comes. i just want the noise to stop. i want to be able to just... stop. does that even make sense? like, is it even wrong to just want everything to be quiet?",
